white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Ambient Lighting<\/span><\/h3><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Pendant holders with diffused shades or frosted glass provide general illumination, softening the overall lighting in a room. When placed strategically, they eliminate harsh shadows and create a welcoming environment.<\/span><\/p><h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 4pt; margin-top: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Task Lighting<\/span><\/h3><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Task lighting is essential for areas where precision is needed, such as kitchen counters, study desks, or workstations. Adjustable pendant holders with focused beams can direct light precisely where it's required, improving visibility and efficiency.<\/span><\/p><h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 4pt; margin-top: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-